真是好可怕<br />\n當台灣殯儀師搵得又多，又有專門學位，個個爭住入<br />\n這邊的竟然咁低智，我們的國真強大"},{"pid":"46c1c9a7d86990db649da53d97e489502bdebdc5","tid":1002671,"uid":101165,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T00:27:34.000Z","msg":"最撚憎呢啲女人"},{"pid":"d2f098c135787c60095c28eaaed50f32b24cfd55","tid":1002671,"uid":163801,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T00:51:42.000Z","msg":"個家長搞到個老師停職，係咪要補償返吓？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n起碼送個公司套餐俾老師全家啦！"},{"pid":"06f678a9d69976795841c88a7ad1341f95d69a9f","tid":1002671,"uid":85629,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"quote":{"pid":"d0fee9fb3df3b38ecad811f6cc6bd744f7606c56","tid":1002671,"uid":82291,"like":24,"dislike":5,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T00:26:16.000Z","msg":"無知愚味真是好可怕<br />\n當台灣殯儀師搵得又多，又有專門學位，個個爭住入<br />\n這邊的竟然咁低智，我們的國真強大"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T00:54:01.000Z","msg":"大陸直接拎完器官火化<br />\n殯乜儀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b119646a5b8cd7728c5b2ed8d34e5c7c486d6cf","tid":1002671,"uid":69429,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T01:21:19.000Z","msg":"家長應該叫殯儀界封殺返個老師 睇下邊個大獲啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63c4651b67decaef5f4c1a181109c9995faad32c","tid":1002671,"uid":69289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T01:26:59.000Z","msg":"chinese pig<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba10d2adf0233a23137c93eb7bd537ba2fad8dca","tid":1002671,"uid":80814,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T01:49:08.000Z","msg":"[殘體慎入] <a href=\"https://m.douban.com/group/topic/132168287/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.douban.com%2Fgroup%2Ftopic%2F132168287%2F&d=h41GIreLF%2BIJLuW8J2uc6mmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=1b7a7cee\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.douban.com/group/topic/132168287/</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個教畜唔止咁少嘢，試諗吓本身平時係正常嘅教師點會咁樣純粹因為口臭而杯個學生？<br />\n<br />\n根據教畜啲舊生爆料，佢本身就會要啲學生同家長講要送禮物，咁佢考試前就會識做，透露試題。<br />\n<br />\n同埋中國啲制度仲係班主任係一班惡哂，班長就係佢啲手下，一般學生就係最底層要被奴役，做親班主任都係油水位嚟，而呢個教畜都係有背景嘅。<br />\n<br />\n至於點解一路無人爆佢大鑊，就係啲學生同家長都覺得送禮同巴結佢，就會知道試題，成績好就算喇。中國嘅教育就係咁扭曲，就算喺一班入面都係咁腐敗。<br />\n<br />\n同埋之前有另一個教畜因為話唔見支唇膏，屈個班入面最窮嘅學生偷，再叫其他學生打到人地可能以後都生唔到，好可能都係做開呢啲嘢。"},{"pid":"5af816e4be1d4f5b86339e38609ac907a91497fa","tid":1002671,"uid":219803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T01:52:20.000Z","msg":"佢地真係好垃 咁都做得出"},{"pid":"15ff5f04df1baedca45f1e9e4436a032d3c1c8b9","tid":1002671,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"06966e128f88362032ff1369160669230d01d3cd","tid":1002671,"uid":205462,"like":244,"dislike":2,"score":242,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T06:35:10.000Z","msg":"大陸就係最多呢啲生番<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 女學生嘅家長做乜職業，關個女乜事?<br />\n<br />\n吳耀漢話佢細個淨係喺英國被鬼仔凌欺，香港係無人蝦佢，因為佢嗰個年代，香港嘅人百無禁忌，棺材都照瞓可乜"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T01:55:02.000Z","msg":"香港d小學教畜其實唔好得幾多，係唔敢做咁揚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04516e9ea1a8e96445d4f09336849590579b681a","tid":1002671,"uid":80814,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T02:05:15.000Z","msg":"好多其他中文媒體，報道中國啲新聞都剩係得表面嘅嘢，講最Juicy嘅部分，忽略點解一個教師都會有咁嘅權力。<br />\n<br />\n呢啲唔係咩唔文明，讀得少書同落後而做成，呢個係結構問題。極權政府為咗完全操控被統治者，去揀邊啲係最底層，邊啲係有權力去剝削下一層，咁就分化到佢地。<br />\n<br />\n所以無人會想反黨，個個都爭住做剝削人嗰個，最底層嗰班掛住生存，連咩係人嘅尊嚴同權利都唔得閒知。<br />\n<br />\n基本上無得救，無可能會自己變返好。"},{"pid":"bce275f6b43a9b11327ffe481cfd5b49416fb2ab","tid":1002671,"uid":80814,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"15ff5f04df1baedca45f1e9e4436a032d3c1c8b9","tid":1002671,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"06966e128f88362032ff1369160669230d01d3cd","tid":1002671,"uid":205462,"like":244,"dislike":2,"score":242,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T06:35:10.000Z","msg":"大陸就係最多呢啲生番<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 女學生嘅家長做乜職業，關個女乜事?<br />\n<br />\n吳耀漢話佢細個淨係喺英國被鬼仔凌欺，香港係無人蝦佢，因為佢嗰個年代，香港嘅人百無禁忌，棺材都照瞓可乜"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T01:55:02.000Z","msg":"香港d小學教畜其實唔好得幾多，係唔敢做咁揚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T02:14:29.000Z","msg":"香港教師都爭perm位，contract就係被壓榨嘅一群，為咗轉正要刷鞋埋堆應該好常見。仲有唔畀港獨思想滲透校園呢？自己已經要愛國愛港先，仲確保自己教嘅學生思想要正確<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f45d9e07880aaf2b7d984bbf2e3fdbcda669a07c","tid":1002671,"uid":76470,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T02:26:17.000Z","msg":"知道有家長做殯儀咪仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到自己/屋企有咩事搵人做唔洗比人劏嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"badcb5ea54310c6dfc5328b11160c0a16710cbbb","tid":1002671,"uid":6222,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T02:29:55.000Z","msg":"祝有份欺凌佢嘅人全家死哂都無人收屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n條屍比狗食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc35abc472b24d86f4bc12a7c0952125d4f8fa73","tid":1002671,"uid":81190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T02:32:30.000Z","msg":"又話無神論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fd5ce67411990cdb908e7eb8f4dbccef24a19f8","tid":1002671,"uid":62935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T02:34:29.000Z","msg":"野人社會"},{"pid":"cdc43045f6e5b274453c182c08a48e951c1d2987","tid":1002671,"uid":33643,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T02:37:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.nvsay.com/uploads/allimg/190130/214-1Z130125532I6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nvsay.com%2Fuploads%2Fallimg%2F190130%2F214-1Z130125532I6.jpg&h=66b1e6f0&s={SIZE}\"